headline: Trump to impose 25% tariff on trucks starting Nov. 1
summary: President Donald Trump will impose a 25% tariff on imported medium- and heavy-duty trucks starting Nov. 1. The post Trump to impose 25% tariff on trucks starting Nov. 1 appeared first on FreightWaves.

headline: Allison Transmission 4500 RDS Model Now Pairs with Cummins X15N Natural Gas Engine, Delivering Enhanced Performance and Efficiency
summary: Allison Transmission is proud to announce its 4500 Rugged Duty Series (RDS) fully automatic transmission has been successfully integrated with the Cummins X15N natural gas engine in Kenworth T880 tractors. The pairing sets a new standard for sustainable heavy-duty transportation, delivering exceptional power and innovative technology.

headline: A Fresh Look at Terex (TEX) Valuation After Recent Zacks Rank Upgrade and Analyst Optimism
summary: Terex (TEX) has caught investors’ attention following its upgrade to a Zacks Rank #2 (Buy). Recent analyst optimism about the company’s earnings prospects has fueled a positive shift in the stock’s outlook. See our latest analysis for Terex. Alongside its Zacks Rank upgrade, Terex recently welcomed Srikanth Padmanabhan, a veteran leader from Cummins, to its Board of Directors.
